    "description": "<strong>Escape the sewer</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/3269017d0e95076b448b1dc6360a1c87.poster.avif?t=1746424810\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/3269017d0e95076b448b1dc6360a1c87.webm?t=1746424810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/3269017d0e95076b448b1dc6360a1c87.mp4?t=1746424810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Do you have what it takes to reach the top? In Septic, you are thrust into the depths of an underground sewer system. With its responsive controls and demanding jumps, this first-person platformer will test your agility and precision at every turn. Navigate through treacherous environments and aim to escape the murky depths.<br><br><strong>Don't fall</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/b49c22f5768ba84ee8effae7b80bb64a.poster.avif?t=1746424810\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/b49c22f5768ba84ee8effae7b80bb64a.webm?t=1746424810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146010/extras/b49c22f5768ba84ee8effae7b80bb64a.mp4?t=1746424810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A single misstep could lead to a devastating fall, costing you tons of progress. The stakes are high, and the margin for error is slim. Each jump must be perfectly timed and executed. Stay focused and don’t let the pressure get to you, or you might find yourself back at the bottom, starting all over again.<br><br><strong>Master the Mechanics</strong><br>Septic challenges you to master its intricate mechanics. Every movement, from the simplest jump to the most complex maneuver, requires precision and skill. The responsive controls are designed to give you full command over your actions, allowing you to hone your abilities and achieve perfection. Practice makes perfect, and perfection is the key to survival.<br><br><strong>Endure the Challenge</strong><br>Prepare yourself for an intense and unforgiving journey. Septic ramps up the difficulty as you progress, presenting you with relentless obstacles and increasingly complex levels. Your perseverance and determination will be tested like never before. Only the most resilient players will endure the challenge and emerge victorious.",
